    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="T48n2025-start">
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s1" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-20T12:02:29.968+09:00">夫学般若菩薩、先当起大悲心、発弘誓願、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s2" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-20T12:04:01.923+09:00">精修三昧、誓度衆生、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s3" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-20T12:04:59.317+09:00">不為一身独求解脱爾。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s4" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-20T12:39:01.993+09:00">乃放捨諸緑、休息万事、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s5" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-20T12:39:25.637+09:00">身心一如、動静無間、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s6" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-20T12:40:41.044+09:00">其飲食、不多不少、調其睡眠、不節不恣。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s7" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-20T13:22:27.895+09:00">欲坐禅時、於閑静処、厚敷坐物、寛繋衣帯、令威儀斉整、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s8" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-20T13:26:40.372+09:00">然後結跏趺坐。先以右足安左陛上、左足安右陛上。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s9" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-20T13:42:49.187+09:00">或半跏趺坐亦可、但以左足圧右足而已。次以右手安左足上、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s10" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-20T13:35:25.575+09:00">左掌安右掌上、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s11" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-20T13:29:40.799+09:00">両手大拇指面相柱、徐徐挙身前欠、復左右揺振、</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T48n2025_CBETA_005-1143a0401.s12" xml:lang="en" resp="#Francisco" modified="2025-03-20T13:30:13.87+09:00">乃正身端坐。</seg>
                </p>
